Package: sotk2
Type: Package
Title: Spatial omics toolkit for cross-platform module integration
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Heewon",
           family = "Seo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "Heewon.Seo@UCalgary.ca")
Description: sotk2 is an R package for integrating omics datasets using modules derived from
    non-negative matrix factorization (NMF) or consensus NMF (cNMF). The workflow
    concatenates basis (W) matrices across ranks and datasets, computes metageneâ€“metagene
    correlations, constructs a correlation network, and applies community detection to
    identify integrative biological modules. sotk2 also supports rank inspection through
    community coverage plots and provides utilities for gene-level interpretation via
    metagene-associated genes (MAGs) and contributing community genes.
